  "detailed_description": "<h1>Buzz</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284300/extras/cb2edd0a7aef720604efb1b54c1f340c.avif?t=1643797787\" width=599 height=246 /></span><br>“King of Spies” is a political spy-thriller visual novel and yuri dating sim.  You play as Kelly Bond, a former USAF Intelligence Officer turned political espionage specialist. Infiltrate a rising political star’s campaign and discover their deepest secrets as your mission will decide the country’s fate forever!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284300/extras/7342d2b6da2fe9f81d5815faf9c161f1.webp?t=1643797787\" width=598 height=56 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A gripping political espionage and romance storyline.<br></li><li>Soothing contemporary jazz soundtrack<br></li><li>Beautiful anime art<br></li><li>Multiple endings</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284300/extras/cb2edd0a7aef720604efb1b54c1f340c.avif?t=1643797787\" width=599 height=246 /></span><br>“King of Spies” is a political spy-thriller visual novel and yuri dating sim.  You play as Kelly Bond, a former USAF Intelligence Officer turned political espionage specialist. Infiltrate a rising political star’s campaign and discover their deepest secrets as your mission will decide the country’s fate forever!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1284300/extras/7342d2b6da2fe9f81d5815faf9c161f1.webp?t=1643797787\" width=598 height=56 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A gripping political espionage and romance storyline.<br></li><li>Soothing contemporary jazz soundtrack<br></li><li>Beautiful anime art<br></li><li>Multiple endings</li></ul>",
